ðŸ”¹ Part 3: Add Users to Groups
Task 4: Add user1 & user2 to projectA
sudo usermod -aG projectA user1
sudo usermod -aG projectA user2
Task 5: Add user3 to projectB
sudo usermod -aG projectB user3







Task 6: Verify group membership
id user1
id user2
id user3
